        "id": 3,
        "title": "CTL Ramp Rate (week-over-week fitness change)",
        "description": "How fast your fitness (CTL) is changing. A safe ramp is 3-5 points/week. Above 7 significantly increases injury and illness risk. Negative means you're losing fitness.",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 8,
          "w": 24,
          "x": 0,
          "y": 33
